拍抖音，我偶尔刷到才知道这个人，视频内容基本就是今天做什么赚了多少钱卖了多少钱和小孩。</p>\n<p>但是昨天下午他羊棚子起火，十几分钟全烧完，死了两百多头羊，救都救不赢，他人也是直接晕厥过去了。</p>\n<p>我把这事在群里一说，本来是想感叹城市套路多，农村有坏人（他家羊棚子没有线路，监控流量没续费看不了回放，我比较倾向村里有人眼红做的），吃一个套路讲教训，碰到坏人那是真的翻不了身，后面大家就讨论  在家里（承包田做养殖+补贴+做的其他的+类似那男的做的事）是否比城里打工能赚钱了</p>\n<p>我是觉得在家里做糊口差不多，赚是赚不了什么钱，在外面打工省点还是能存到钱的</p>\n", "last_modified": 1728369386, "replies": 117, "id": 1078260}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 26748, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3031, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 683522, "username": "aaxaax", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/aaxaax", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_mini.png?m=1723084531", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_normal.png?m=1723084531", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_large.png?m=1723084531", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_xlarge.png?m=1723084531", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_xlarge.png?m=1723084531", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_xlarge.png?m=1723084531", "created": 1712120057, "last_modified": 1723084531}, "last_reply_by": "irever", "last_touched": 1728446294, "title": "苹果手机信号为什么一直这么差？改进一下很难吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1078422", "created": 1728434379, "