949, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 242713, "username": "kokerkov", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kokerkov", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/394276fe32a121c5c21b4af110058c98?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/394276fe32a121c5c21b4af110058c98?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/394276fe32a121c5c21b4af110058c98?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1500525842, "last_modified": 1728362110}, "last_reply_by": "niaohongC", "last_touched": 1728423941, "title": "不是很懂 NAS，有点问题想问一下。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1078236", "created": 1728362123, "deleted": 0, "content": "需求：（优先级逐次递减）\r\n\r\n\t1.存储孩子视频和文件 \r\n    2.影音库 \r\n    3.游戏库（各种模拟器） \r\n    4.文件库。\r\n\r\n以下问题皆基于以上需求而提出。\r\n\r\n问题：\r\n\r\n\t1. 各个 NAS 品牌之间的区别主要是什么呢？操作系统吗？那我拿来刷其他开源系统，甚至直接装 linux/Windows Server 也可以的呀。不会有硬件像手机一样锁 BL 的吧？\r\n    2. 预算有限，打算买便宜的绿联之类的。他们会不会系统偷偷传数据给他们服务器？（非遥测必需数据）", "content_rendered": "<p>需求：（优先级逐次递减）</p>\n<pre><code>1.存储孩子视频和文件 \n2.影音库 \n3.游戏库（各种模拟器） \n4.文件库。\n</code></pre>\n<p>以下问题皆基于以上需求而提出。</p>\n<p>问题：</p>\n<pre><code>1. 各个 NAS 品牌之间的区别主要是什么呢？操作系统吗？那我拿来刷其他开源系统，甚至直接装 linux/Windows Server 也可以的呀。不会有硬件像手机一样锁 BL 的吧？\n2. 预算有限，打算买便宜的绿联之类的。他们会不会系统偷偷传数据给他们服务器？（非遥测必需数据）\n</code></pre>\n", "last_modified": 1728362123, "replies": 68, "id": 1078236}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 223712, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4243, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 635747, "username": "wcy0